text: The Easter Island moray (Gymnothorax nasuta) is a moray eel found in the southeast Pacific Ocean, around Easter Island and Chile.Gymnothorax nasuta at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by de Buen in 1961.Common names for Gymnothorax nasuta at www.fishbase.org. ==References== nasuta Category:Fish described in 1961
